MC2 seems to cluster together, but MC1 is scattered without any clear clustering. There are 171 total differentially expressed genes (padj < 0.05)

Below are the top 20 differentially expressed genes.

528 pathways were found to be significantly differentially enriched (padj < 0.05) with the C2 curated gene sets from the Human MSigDB Collections, converted to mouse orthologs with the msigdbr package.
